msgctxt "option:check"
msgid "Automatically log in:"
msgstr "Saio-haste automatikoa:"

#: src/ui/Advanced.qml:28
#, kde-format
msgctxt ""
"@label:listbox, the following combobox selects the user to log in "
"automatically"
msgid "as user:"
msgstr "erabiltzaile hau gisa:"

#: src/ui/Advanced.qml:92
#, kde-format
msgctxt ""
"@label:listbox, the following combobox selects the session that is started "
"automatically"
msgid "with session"
msgstr "saio honekin,"

#: src/ui/Advanced.qml:124
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"Auto-login does not support unlocking your KDE Wallet automatically, so it "
"will ask you to unlock it every time you log in.<nl/><nl/>To avoid this, you "
"can change the wallet to have a blank password. Note that this is insecure "
"and should only be done in a trusted environment."
msgstr ""
"Saio-haste automatikoak ez du zure KDE Zorroa automatikoki giltzaz "
"irekitzeko euskarririk, hori dela eta saio-hasten duzun guztietan hori "
"egiteko eskatuko dizu.<nl/><nl/>Hori saihesteko, zorroa alda dezakezu "
"pasahitza hutsik izan dezan. Kontuan izan hau ez dela segurua eta konfiantza "
"duen ingurune batean baino ez litzateke egin behar."

#: src/ui/Advanced.qml:129
#, kde-format
msgid "Open KDE Wallet Settings"
msgstr "Ireki KDE Zorroaren ezarpenak"

#: src/ui/Advanced.qml:135
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:check"
msgid "Log in again immediately after logging off"
msgstr "Saio-hasi saioa itxi eta berehala"

